title: Who Has Higher Testosterone: Bobby or Lunchbox? + We Crown A March Riddle Master + Name That Country Artist: St. Patrick’s Day Edition!
itunes:title: Who Has Higher Testosterone: Bobby or Lunchbox? + We Crown A March Riddle Master + Name That Country Artist: St. Patrick’s Day Edition!
description:
Lunchbox sent in a story about how men with high testosterone levels less GENEROUS are more likely to display selfish behaviors. It leads into a debate on who we think has more testosterone between Bobby and Lunchbox. We play a round of Riddle Me This for the month of March. We celebrate St. Patrick’s Day with a game of Name that Country Artist! Can you name the artist wishing you a happy St. Patrick’s Day?

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
